teetime.framework

Class AbstractStage

  • java.lang.Object
    • teetime.framework.AbstractStage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractConsumerStage, AbstractProducerStage, Delay, DivideAndConquerCombineStage, DivideAndConquerDivideStage, DivideAndConquerSolveStage, DivideAndConquerStage, Merger

    public abstract class AbstractStage
extends Object
    Represents a minimal Stage, with some pre-defined methods. Implemented stages need to adapt all abstract methods with own implementations.
